Installing in debian ( Lenny amd64 ):

A. Preparing
    0. What do You need?
        libspeex-dev
        libspeexdsp-dev

B. Creating necessary libs ( sources in src/external )    
    0. Set compiler flags:
	export CFLAGS="-fPIC -march=athlon64" ( for amd64 )
    
    1. Compile ffmpeg
        cd ffmpeg
        git pull
        ./configure --enable-shared
        make
        sudo make install

	cd libswscale
	git pull
	make
	sudo make install
    
    2. Compile linphone
	cd linphone-cvs
	cvs up
	./autogen.sh
	./configure
	